title: Overprotective dad shows daughter's date who's boss in...
text:
By HotTopics.tv
BANGOR, Wis. – A dad’s warning to his daughter’s homecoming date is going viral.
Riccarra Schock, 15, of Wisconsin was posing for photos with her date before heading to the dance. Her mother, Sharee Schock, is a professional photographer with Schock Photography , according to ABC News .
Screengrab via Schock Photography / Facebook As Sharee snapped photos, her husband jumped in.
>> Read more trending stories
“My husband said to him in a silly way, ‘Whatever you do, I’m going to do to you,’" Sharee recalled. “It was just meant in a playful fun.”
Benjamin Schock then jumped in the photo behind his daughter’s date and put his arms around his waist.
His daughter laughed it off and later posted the photo to her Instagram account. Her mother says her daughter and her homecoming date are enjoying their newfound fame in their small town.
